-# Generic fallback renderer for an audit event.
-#
-# Locals:
-#   event — a single AuditEvent hash from atlas_rb
-#
-# The `on_behalf_of_nuid` line surfaces a piece-5-era field that's always
-# `nil` today — but reading it now means piece 5 doesn't need to touch
-# this partial at all.
%li.audit-event
  %strong= event['actor_nuid']
  did
  %em= event['action']
  on #{Time.iso8601(event['occurred_at']).strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S UTC')}
  - if event['on_behalf_of_nuid'].present?
    (on behalf of #{event['on_behalf_of_nuid']})
